{"tid":2153574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿：如果泛民總辭 熱狗立法會、區議會議員會跟機","createTime":"2020-08-12T15:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T15:46:42.000Z","uid":156109,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"047a6b4c2ae15e59c8d0a81f3e375f629a2f1d94","tid":2153574,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/794yqZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F794yqZK.png&h=7e942f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果有黃絲朋友問泛民總辭「最佳時機」係幾時，大家可以貼 熱血公民 喺2017年7月14日嘅聲明畀佢哋睇。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">講埋都得，如果泛民真係總辭唔再參與立法會、區議會選舉，熱血公民一位立法會議員、兩位區議員陪你玩又點話。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，黃絲朋友如果想睇總辭，請向泛民施壓。<br />\n<br />\n詳情請參閱今日 Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰 接受傳媒嘅訪問。<br />\n<br />\nnow訪問：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=401424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401424&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=323a8a98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401424&h=d5050844\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=401424</a><br />\n<br />\n有線訪問：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=32720&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D32720%26ct%3D1&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=eda11479\" target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=32720&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"a7283a43517796a4d24a2e4b74fe31a3c3cada7e","tid":2153574,"uid":292789,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:13:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好再貼呢班小丑嘅野？"},{"pid":"9ac9cf0ad0800db682e46099309aceebcbcd8c60","tid":2153574,"uid":156109,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7283a43517796a4d24a2e4b74fe31a3c3cada7e","tid":2153